				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="1"><b>More Exclusive Velious Shots</b></a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:catalyst@everlore.com">Catalyst</b></a>
				[12/1/2000-7:08:35 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=288835"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[5]</font></a>
				<p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
<p>

Cindy Archuleta has again hooked us up some more exclusive shots of the Scars of Velious EverQuest expansion pack. Velious is set to go retail very soon and is one of the most highly anticipated releases this Christmas and is sure to be a hot seller. We've posted eight more high resolution shots from this upcoming masterpiece by Verant, these shots are sure to please.

</p>
<p>
